'''Portaak amber''' was a resin that came from the [[portaak leaf]]. It was a translucent [[Orange (disambiguation)|orange]]-[[Brown (disambiguation)|brown]] in color. A natural fungicide, the [[Korun/Legends|Korunnai]] rubbed their weapons with it to prevent the world's various metal- and [[Silica/Legends|silicate]]-eating [[Fungus/Legends|fungi]] from degrading them. Although sticky, the resin did not rub off on users' hands. Along with [[thyssel bark]] it was an extremely lucrative trade for jungle prospectors.<ref name="Shatterpoint">[[Shatterpoint (novel)]]</ref>

